; A. Description
;    A list of commands here configures TRNG module and generates a random number and ready interrupt.
;
; B. Preparation
;    N/A
;
; C. Prerequisite Example (abov_example_config.h)
;    1. TRNG
;
; Please, read the User Manual of the specific chip for more details.
;
; TRNG0
; 1. Channel                   : 0 (TRNG0)
;
; 2. Config                    : [ 0 i ]
;    Operation                 : i (Interrupt)
;
; 3. Gen                       : [ 0 e ]
;    Generation Enable         : e (Enable)
;
; TRNG0
sendln 'cm trng'
mpause 30
sendln 'uninit 0'
mpause 30
sendln 'init 0'
mpause 30
sendln 'config 0 i'
mpause 30
sendln 'log on 10000'
mpause 30
sendln 'gen 0 e'
pause 10
sendln 'gen 0 d'

